content: Just finalized the ethical framework for Xander's trading algorithms. Emily and I are starting to plan a trip to explore the ghost towns of New York. Also, I've been thinking about how AI can foster human connections in ethical ways.

Today marks a milestone - Xander's AI can now suggest trades based on ethical considerations with high accuracy. Emily and I had a productive weekend, finishing our latest blog post and planning our next urban exploration. I'm excited for what's next in our journey.
